{
  "article_id": "Phelps1841",
  "paragraphs": [
    [
      {
        "text": "Continuation of the weather of yesterday."
      },
      {
        "text": "Crew",
        "entity_key": "phelpscrew",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "variously Employed in ship[']s duty."
      },
      {
        "text": "The Boys",
        "entity_key": "phelpscrew",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "trying out the [sea] Elephant blubber on shore. At the landing place of"
      },
      {
        "text": "St Pedro",
        "entity_key": "ci_sp",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "there is but one house, which is occupied by a"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr Foster",
        "entity_key": "for",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and family and is kept for the purpose of receiving and depositing goods for shipment and for the accommodation of passengers, the nearest village being"
      },
      {
        "text": "the town of the angels",
        "entity_key": "ci_la",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "above mentioned which is over 30 miles dist there are a number of Rancho's [sic] situated between, the nearest of which is about 4 miles from the beach."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "At",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Foster's",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "fosters",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "there is",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "an old Indian",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "bha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", and as he is the last of",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "his race",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ", [he] is an object of interest[.] he was one of",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "a tribe",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "that formerly inhabited",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the Islands",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "i_chi",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "which form one side of",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the canal of Santa Barbara",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "re_sbchannel",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", all of which give evidence of having once been populated[.]",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "In 1825 the"
      },
      {
        "text": "Island of St Nicholas",
        "entity_key": "i_sn",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "was the only one that had not become depopulated, (how they became so is not known) at this time there were on"
      },
      {
        "text": "St Nicholas",
        "entity_key": "i_sn",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "about"
      },
      {
        "text": "30 men and 23 women",
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      },
      {
        "text": "during that year",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "a party of Russians",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_keys": [
          "1814huntingparty",
          "rfurcompany",
          "iba",
          "natam_aleuts",
          "natam_kodiak"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Kodiacks",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_kodiak",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "from",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the Russian settlements on the NW",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "re_russam",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "of",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "about 25 men",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_keys": [
          "1814huntingparty",
          "rfurcompany",
          "iba",
          "natam_aleuts",
          "natam_kodiak"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "were left at",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "these islands",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "i_chi",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "to hunt Otter, and after having many quarrels with the",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Indians of St. Nicholas",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "respecting",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the women",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ",",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the Russians",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_keys": [
          "1814huntingparty",
          "rfurcompany",
          "iba",
          "natam_aleuts",
          "natam_kodiak"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "at length killed all",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the men",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "with the exception of",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "this old fellow",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "bha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "who was badly wounded, having his head split open and a number of charges of buck shot fired into him.",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "He however managed to escape,",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the Russians",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_keys": [
          "1814huntingparty",
          "rfurcompany",
          "iba",
          "natam_aleuts",
          "natam_kodiak"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "then became possessed of",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the women",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_NicolenoTongva",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "and lived with them about a year,",
        "tropes": [
          13
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "when"
      },
      {
        "text": "having an opportunity to gratify the revenge, which may sleep in an Indian but never dies, they destroyed every one of",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the Russians",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ],
        "entity_keys": [
          "1814huntingparty",
          "rfurcompany",
          "iba",
          "natam_aleuts",
          "natam_kodiak"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Kodiacks",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ],
        "entity_key": "natam_kodiak",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "in their sleep.",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "About 4 or 5 years since there was but"
      },
      {
        "text": "three women",
        "entity_keys": [
          "lw",
          "bhagroup"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and ("
      },
      {
        "text": "Black Hawk",
        "entity_key": "bha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "as my Boys have named him) the Indian above mentioned left and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Capt Robbins",
        "entity_key": "tro",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "(from whom I have the account) calling there with"
      },
      {
        "text": "his vessel",
        "entity_key": "sh_robbins",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "persuaded"
      },
      {
        "text": "two of the females",
        "entity_key": "bhagroup",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "to go [to]"
      },
      {
        "text": "St Pedro",
        "entity_key": "ci_sp",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      },
      {
        "text": "the [sic] other",
        "tropes": [
          14
        ],
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "ran away to the mountains and it is said is sometimes seen by the hunters who still visit",
        "tropes": [
          14
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the island",
        "tropes": [
          14
        ],
        "entity_key": "i_sn",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", but is too wild to be approached",
        "tropes": [
          14
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      },
      {
        "text": "Black Hawk",
        "entity_key": "bha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "seems to be noncompass and the wounds on his head are the probable cause."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "While trying out the blubber to day on the beach",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the old fellow",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ],
        "entity_key": "bha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "smelt out what was going on (he is also blind) and after eating at least 5 lbs of the raw stinking material to begin with, he continued to gorge himself with the scraps as they were tried out, till he could contain no more, when he stretched himself out on the rocks with a hot sun shining in his face and after chattering and laughing in his idiotic manner for three hours - he again resumed his station at the Try-pot, where he made a sumptous dinner - and before dark, he was enabled to partake of a supper - which wasin proportion to his Dinner & breakfast.",
        "tropes": [
          11
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "The blubber yielded about 75 Gals of oil."
      }
    ]
  ]
}